title: Kim v0.11.0
description: Kim is an open world RPG set in Rudyard Kipling's colonial India. Play as his ragamuffin hero Kim and roam hand-painted towns and procedurally generated countryside. Learn to survive as a penniless urchin, complete objectives, collect items and garner favour with the spies of the secret service. Live Kim's youth as best you can for it is fleeting but if at first you don't succeed, you may retell this classic tale as often as you wish
